# Comments for Team Reference
#########################
# Files to include in version control:
# - All .rego policy files
# - Terraform configuration templates
# - Documentation and README files
# - CI/CD workflow definitions
# - Test files and examples
# - Scripts (but not their output)

# Files to never commit:
# - Terraform state files (contain sensitive data)
# - AWS credentials or API keys
# - Terraform plan outputs (contain sensitive data)
# - Any files with passwords or secrets
# - Personal IDE configurations
# - Operating system generated files

# Optional files (team decision):
# - .terraform.lock.hcl (some teams commit, others don't)
# - terraform.tfvars (if it contains only non-sensitive defaults)
# - IDE workspace files (if team uses same IDE)

# Note: This .gitignore is designed for a Policy as Code project
# using Terraform and OPA. Adjust based on your team's needs
# and security requirements.